			[1091] heading 'Setting Up a Cron Job'
			[1093] paragraph ''
				StaticText "If you want to automatically update your tweets you'll need to set up a cron job. You can find more information on Cron elsewhere, but here's an example that will run your cron.php every hour of the day:"

			[1107] paragraph ''

				StaticText 'To import the archive follow these steps:'
